OL,3,CMan, 36, accused of punching
OL,4,Cgrandfather outside pub denies murder
OL,6,FA man accused of punching a 66-year-
OL,7,Fold outside a pub in Leicestershire
OL,8,Fhas denied murder.
OL,10,FNathan Gothard, aged 36, appeared at
OL,11,FLeicester Crown Court on Tuesday to
OL,12,Fdeny one count of murder.
OL,14,FDavid Darke died in hospital after
OL,15,Fsustaining a serious head injury
OL,16,Foutside the Crown Inn in Appleby Magna
OL,17,Fon the 21 December last year.
