OL,6,FHe spoke only to confirm his name and
OL,7,Fenter his plea during the 10-minute
OL,8,Fhearing in front of Judge William
OL,9,FHarbage KC.
OL,11,FGothard, of Church Street, Appleby
OL,12,FMagna, was told he would face a trial
OL,13,Flasting seven days on 27th of April.
OL,15,FJudge Harbage told the defendant in
OL,16,Fthe dock: "Stand up please, Nathan
OL,17,FGothard ` you have pleaded not guilty
OL,18,Fto the charge against you.
