OL,6,F"You are aware it is a very serious
OL,7,Fcharge. There will be a trial, that
OL,8,Fhas already been fixed for April 27.
OL,9,FIn the meantime, you will be remanded
OL,10,Fin custody."
OL,12,FThe judge said he was aware an
OL,13,Fapplication for bail would be made in
OL,14,Fdue course on behalf of the defendant
OL,15,Fbut that he was not going to decide
OL,16,Fthe "merits" of that at Tuesday's
OL,17,Fhearing.
