OL,6,FIn a statement released through
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police after his death,
OL,8,FMr Darke's family said: "Dave was a
OL,9,Fdeeply-loved father to three daughters
OL,10,Fand a proud grandfather to three boys.
OL,12,F"He was a much-loved brother and a
OL,13,Fdear friend. Dave will live on forever
OL,14,Fin our hearts, minds and souls.
OL,16,F"He was a strong, active, intelligent
OL,17,Fand kind person who was a friend to
OL,18,Fall.
