OL,6,F"He was a devoted family man with a
OL,7,Fdeep passion for life, the outdoors,
OL,8,Fnature and walking.
OL,10,F"His life was tragically cut short and
OL,11,Fhe's now reunited with his loving,
OL,12,Fcaring parents. He will be sorely
OL,13,Fmissed by all who knew and loved him."
